description.narrative:
The main objective of the Core support to Biotica is the institutional development of the association and the shift from project-based towards a mission-driven organization. In this way, the within the core support, Biotica will implement its strategy for the period 2022-2025 and the corresponding Results Assessment Framework. The three major outcomes that Biotica is working towards are: 

1) Improved conditions for biodiversity by rehabilitation of ecosystems, safeguarding endangered species, and promotion of sustainable development; 
2) Raised resilience of the communities from target areas; 
3) Consolidation of internal capacities and partnerships. 

Biotica will work Central and Local Public Authorities, academia, businesses, CSOs and general public on increasing the understanding of importance and protection of biodiversity. Also, Biotica will conducts small-scale infrastructure improvement of ecosystems, will draft and participate in consultation of draft legal acts and local plans, will develop relevant studies.
